data.description: JUST REDUCED! This 3/2 pool home is a rare find in an excellent location and highly desired neighborhood. No HOA. Like countryside in the city! Home is on cul-de-sac, fenced in, covered patio overlooking the pool. Modernized layout, remodeled in 2019. Beautiful kitchen with granite counters and island. Extended kitchen area with fridge makes the space look bigger. Bonus room can become a playroom, office or gym. Beautiful Pool is 17.5 x 30 surrounded by tropical plants, vegetation makes it private. Concrete pool shed is 10x12. Playground seen on pictures and pool equipment stays. Comfortable distance to nice schools, shopping areas, restaurants and diverse places of worship. About 5 miles from Turnpike. Newer garage door. New water softener system in 2020. All windows have hurricane shutters. Do you have big toys? Bring them all! This house has spacious parking for RV, boat, trailer, service/business vehicles, motorcycles, bikes, and more. It will all fit in this private backyard!
